article.description: — Darius McGhee had 22 points as Liberty easily defeated North Florida 80-60 on Saturday.
article.headline: McGhee scores 22 to lead Liberty over North Florida 80-60
article.linkText: McGhee scores 22 to lead Liberty over North Florida 80-60
article.story: LYNCHBURG, Va. -- — Darius McGhee had 22 points as Liberty easily defeated North Florida 80-60 on Saturday. Chris Parker had 13 points for Liberty (17-5, 8-2 Atlantic Sun Conference), which earned its sixth straight victory. Kyle Rode added 10 points, eight rebounds and five assists. Carter Hendricksen had 18 points for the Ospreys (7-13, 5-5) and Jose Placer added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
